Effects of Spells

1.Spark=Electric Damage
2.Ice=Ice Damage
3.Fire Ball=Fire Damage
4.Shadow=Dark Damage
5.Doom Blades=Wind Damage
6.Earth Spike=Earth Damage
7.Flame Spike=Fire Damage
8.Blizzard=Ice Damage
9.Lightning=Electric Damage
10.FireStorm=Fire Damage
11.Twister=Wind Damage
12.Power Wave=Electric Damage
13.Confuse=Makes target randomly move against will.
14.Mega Heal=Makes target or caster heal quickly
15.Stone=Lessens the targets chance to Dodge Attacks.
16.Slow=Lessens the targets chance to have quadruple or triple attacks.
17.Silence=Puts targets Spell Power to 0 for a minute or two.
18.Degeneration=Puts targets Regeneration to 0 for a minute or two
19.Apocolypse=Dark Damage
20.Stone Crush=Earth Damage

